http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1830404.mkv&play_token=Rlj4QNu0js&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/3zWj356Tr4SyWdgnZ0qGYc6m5v7.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Lucía is arrested while driving her boyfriend Héctor's car at 200 km/h, dazed and bloody. She was sharing a weekend at the beach with him and Elena, her best friend. Now they are both missing and Lucía only remembers a “little” argument that ended with a bottle broken on Héctor’s head, but that’s all. This complicates Simon’s life. A private investigator? No. , thank you. Simon prefers to consider himself a simple “judicial expert”. When his partner Oliver, a lawyer with financial problems due to gambling, asks him to investigate Lucía and the disappearances, Simon does not know that he is about to take the Expertise on another level. Obsessed with Bogart's film noir, Simón will go beyond all limits when he falls in love with Lucía, the amnesiac suspect in the murder he is investigating." year="2024-11-08" director="Alberto Utrera" actors="Susana Abaitua, Hugo Silva, Julián Villagrán, Rodrigo Poisón, Angelo Olivier",Desmontando a Lucía (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1830400.mkv&play_token=izqWxGeuAd&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/nO4t5lUWQNoSsV8Pt8s0UUYuHk3.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Un astronauta lucha por mantener el control sobre la realidad a bordo de una importante misión hacia Titán, la luna de Saturno. En lo profundo del universo, una tripulación de tres hombres avanza hacia el borde de nuestro sistema solar, una misión que es la única esperanza de la humanidad para resolver una terrible crisis energética." year="2024-08-30" director="Mikael Håfström" actors="Casey Affleck, Laurence Fishburne, Emily Beecham, Tomer Capone, David Morrissey, Charlotta Lövgren, Mark Ebulue, Nikolett Barabas, Harry Szovik",ES - Destino: Titán (HQ) (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1826344.mkv&play_token=hZysSYiBy2&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/iK5rrNUSNUMOWyPUQAHo6WsjOho.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="As Minister of Propaganda, Joseph Goebbels creates films and pictures used to prepare the Germans for Total War and the Holocaust. When the war is lost, he conceives his last staging, the most radical propaganda act still possible to him." year="2024-07-11" director="Klaus Pridnig, Nikolaus Kantner, Kryštof Liška, Marco Rubiero, Jiří Macek" actors="Robert Stadlober, Fritz Karl, Franziska Weisz, Sascha Göpel, Katia Fellin",Führer and Seducer (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1816605.mkv&play_token=3P2Wdmhhp3&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/llWl3GtNoXosbvYboelmoT459NM.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="New York, early 1960s. Against the backdrop of a vibrant music scene and tumultuous cultural upheaval, an enigmatic 19-year-old from Minnesota arrives in the West Village with his guitar and revolutionary talent, destined to change the course of American music." year="2024-12-18" director="James Mangold, Sheila Waldron, Doug Torres, Brad Robinson, Justin Bischoff" actors="Timothée Chalamet, Edward Norton, Elle Fanning, Monica Barbaro, Scoot McNairy",A Complete Unknown (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1814418.mkv&play_token=Ee7f554nRw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/fk09Rg7OWGWRgX2c2GE73UhV7Aj.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="El hogar de Teresa, habitado por ella y su suegra, recibe las visitas de sus hijas en una reunión familiar en el hogar para conmemorar el aniversario de la muerte del padre. Las distintas personalidades de las hermanas -serán el detonante de múltiples conflictos, que provocarán que las protagonistas choquen entre sí y lidien a su vez con sus propias frustraciones, miedos y anhelos." year="2024-11-08" director="Carolina África" actors="Carmen Machi, Bárbara Lennie, Irene Escolar, Victoria Luengo, Beatriz Grimaldos, Lola Cordón, Antonio Resines, Silvia Marsó, Nacho Fresneda",ES - Verano en diciembre (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1814094.mkv&play_token=3DwEbI0DwO&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vbodTEtvoeqCUgY9F74GlWclEBN.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Un granjero anciano se muda a la ciudad urbana por primera vez en su vida. Se hace amigo de un repartidor de papel en el vecindario y su conexión cambia el curso de sus vidas y la familia del niño." year="2024-04-03" director="Ninna Pálmadóttir" actors="Þröstur Leó Gunnarsson, Hermann Samúelsson, Anna Gunndís Guðmundsdóttir, Hjörtur Jóhann Jónsson, Jóel Sæmundsson, Jónmundur Grétarsson, Ahd Tamimi, Asgeir Gunnarsson, Iðunn Ösp Hlynsdóttir",ES - Solitude (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1814052.mkv&play_token=OUV5xOPAI0&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/kAQA0Ftb3kxSUgoo4eQkHoA7rpz.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Irune, una mujer insegura, solitaria y con tendencias hipocondríacas, trabaja en una fábrica de papel situada en las afueras de un pueblo industrial en Álava. Su vida se limita a un reducido círculo de conocidos: sus compañeros de trabajo, una vecina con la que comparte algo parecido a una amistad y un operador de Renfe a quien consulta horarios de trenes que nunca toma. Su frágil equilibrio estallará cuando se detecte un bulto en un pecho, lo que coincidirá con un conflicto laboral en el que se ve implicada. Es entonces cuando su vida toma un giro inesperado, ofreciéndole la oportunidad que, quizás sin saberlo, siempre había estado esperando." year="2024-09-23" director="David Pérez Sañudo" actors="Miren Gaztañaga, Maica Barroso, Erik Probanza, Itziar Aizpuru, Ignacio Mateos, Joan Solé Martí, Font García, Ion Zumelaga, Arkaitz Gartziandia",ES - Los últimos románticos (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1813803.mkv&play_token=dimCS8mKlG&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/5pMlwtK0i239fZlWyhT9ZzmYPnu.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Son lives with his father in an old flat with an endless number of rooms and corridors. The grandfather died, but his corpse lies on the sofa in the living room. Guests come to the apartment sometimes for whom the father prepares in different ways and sets the boy up to the same attitude towards the guests. Every day, the father leaves no one knows where, and the boy remains alone and wanders through the corridors of the flat. On one of these walks, a boy hears subdued screams - they come from a room with an iron door. When he tries to see what's happening there through the peephole, his father appears. Son tries to escape but then faces another terror along the way. The boy seeks to find a way out, but his father suppresses all attempts. 'Eternal' is an author film about the problems of a big state transferred to a small, strange family. By design, the film is a reasonably pessimistic metaphor for modern Russia." year="2021-01-01" director="Ivan Shalaev" actors="Ilya Dodonov, Vladimir Dorondov, Eugenijus Guntulionis, Sergey Mavrin, Nikolay Kalinovskiy",Eternal (2021)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1811988.mkv&play_token=0Vkmy6ch6A&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/79euHUJJtfgeGU63ef38KtNjXEn.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="An odyssey through time and memory, centered on a place in New England where—from wilderness, and then, later, from a home—love, loss, struggle, hope and legacy play out between couples and families over generations." year="2024-10-30" director="Robert Zemeckis, Lizzie Pritchard" actors="Tom Hanks, Robin Wright, Paul Bettany, Kelly Reilly, Ellis Grunsell",Here (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1806287.mkv&play_token=i6NWbzUI34&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/jB26CKrdHYbqZPKotbUfieqkbNl.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2024" description="Marcos Tremmer es un exitoso publicista que vive en Madrid, locamente enamorado de su mujer, Lucía. Un día, Marcos descubre que una enfermedad mortal acabará con su vida en pocos meses." year="2024-11-29" director="Miguel García de la Calera" actors="Benjamín Vicuña, Adriana Ugarte, Félix Gómez, Daniel Hendler, Mirta Busnelli, Hony Estrella, Irene Ferreiro, Julián Valcárcel, Enrique Villén, Rodolfo Castañares",ES - El silencio de Marcos Tremmer (2024)
